"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-sport-other-sport-2024-0712-1459563-saudi-arabia-to-host-first-ever-olympics-esports-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Saudi Arabia will host the inaugural Olympics Esports Games in 2025.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 68, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 12, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.999999529048975, \"rank\": 4.7095117258039485e-07, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee (IOC) said on Friday that the partnership with the Saudi National Olympic Committee would be for 12 years.\", \"from\": 70, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 74, \"end\": 111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 157, \"end\": 162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.5088879973214381, \"rank\": 0.8091175628475217, \"text\": \"Saudi\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 163, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999859821856, \"rank\": 1.3022771291773449e-08, \"text\": \"National Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision will be ratified at the IOC Session to be held on the eve of the Olympic Games in Paris, after which work will begin on selecting a host city for the inaugural edition.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 309, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998853009012, \"rank\": 1.146990265113435e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are very fortunate to be able to work with the Saudi NOC on the Olympic Esports Games, because it has great - if not unique - expertise in the field of Esports with all its stakeholders,\\\" said IOC president Thomas Bach.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.5088879973214381, \"rank\": 0.8091175628475217, \"text\": \"Saudi\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 594, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7786655382885796e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thomas Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Bach\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic Esports Games will greatly benefit from this experience.\\\"\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has been looking into Esports for several years and has formed a dedicated commission to find opportunities.\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 698, \"end\": 701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7786655382885796e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2021, it developed the Olympic virtual series, a pilot venture in Esports.\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 888, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are a youthful nation, with over 23 million gamers,\\\" said Prince Abdulaziz bin Turki Al Faisal, the Saudi Minister of Sport.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 959, \"end\": 968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibn_Saud\", \"score\": 0.9032565990092857, \"rank\": 0.10710511345059268, \"text\": \"Abdulaziz\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibn_Saud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ibn_Saud\"}, {\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turki_bin_Faisal_Al_Saud\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Turki Al Faisal\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turki_bin_Faisal_Al_Saud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turki_bin_Faisal_Al_Saud\"}, {\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.5088879973214381, \"rank\": 0.8091175628475217, \"text\": \"Saudi\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our kingdom has become a global hub for professional Esports... this is a natural next step for our young athletes, our country and the global Esports community.\\\"\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, Saudi Arabia launched an annual Esports World Cup with its first edition currently being held in Riyadh from 3 July to 25 August.\", \"from\": 1185, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.999999529048975, \"rank\": 4.7095117258039485e-07, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 1293, \"end\": 1299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riyadh\", \"score\": 0.9999989781143305, \"rank\": 1.0218792842053315e-06, \"text\": \"Riyadh\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riyadh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riyadh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Saudi Arabia has invested large amounts of money into sports including soccer, Formula One, boxing and golf, with critics accusing the country of engaging in \\\"sports-washing\\\" over its human rights record.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1333, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.999999529048975, \"rank\": 4.7095117258039485e-07, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"score\": 0.9999994977007542, \"rank\": 4.998040906975524e-07, \"text\": \"Formula One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Formula_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The kingdom has denied accusations of human rights abuses.\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC has been trying for years to connect with a younger generation of potential Olympics fans, with its traditional Olympics audience base gradually ageing.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1597, \"end\": 1600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7786655382885796e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said a new dedicated structure would have to be created within the organisation that will be separate from the organisational and financial model for the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7786655382885796e-16, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1972, \"end\": 1995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851268295, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\":